"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The use of ax.set_xticklabels() is discouraged because it depends on tick positions. Instead, ax.set_xticks() should be used to set the positions of the ticks, and then ax.set_xticklabels() can be used to set the labels for those positions.\", \"patch\": \"14c14\\n< ax.set_xticklabels(df['x'])\\n---\\n> ax.set_xticks(df['x'])\\n> ax.set_xticklabels(df['x'])\\n\"}"